id: pm-kjbh
title: "GH-449: contracts policy_modes advertises 'enforce' but governance config accepts 'strict' (contract drift)"
description: "Dogfood GH-449: pm contracts advertises policy_modes [off,warn,enforce] but config validation requires 'strict' — agents driving config from contracts hard-fail. Duplicate check: searched policy modes/enforce strict — no existing item."
